.SH NAME
bareai - Inspect bare-metal AI infrastructure


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbareai [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
bareai is a CLI and TUI for solo AI engineers doing AIOps on a single bare-metal box.

.PP
Inspect host resources, GPUs, Docker, and local LLM runtimes (Ollama, vLLM, SGLang, Triton, etc.)
without mutating the system.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for bareai

.PP
\fB-j\fP, \fB--json\fP[=false]
	output in JSON format

.PP
\fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	disable colored output

.PP
\fB--timeout\fP=10s
	timeout for probes and API calls


